opam-version: "1"
maintainer: "contact@ocamlpro.com"
homepage: "http://www.typerex.org/ocp-indent.html"
license: "LGPL"
build: [
  ["./configure" "--prefix" prefix]
  [make]
  [make "install"]
]
remove: [
  ["./configure" "--prefix" prefix]
  [make "uninstall"]
]
depends: [
  "ocp-build" {>= "1.99.6-beta"}
  "cmdliner"
]
post-messages: [
  "OCP-INDENT installed.

To use it from emacs, add the following to your .emacs:
  (add-to-list 'load-path (concat
     (replace-regexp-in-string \"\\n$\" \"\"
        (shell-command-to-string \"opam config var share\"))
     \"/emacs/site-lisp\"))
  (require 'ocp-indent)

To use it from Vim, add to your .vimrc:
  let opamshare=system(\"opam config var share | tr -d '\\n'\")
  execute \"autocmd FileType ocaml source\".opamshare.\"/vim/syntax/ocp-indent.vim\""
  {success}
]
